@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}

<div class="container">
    <h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

    <p>Welcome to ABC Retail!</p>

    <br />
    <p>At ABC Retail, we pride ourselves on delivering an exceptional shopping experience. We are committed to providing high-quality products at competitive prices, with a focus on customer satisfaction.</p>

    <br />

    <h2>Where It All Started:</h2>
    <p>Founded in Cape Town, our journey began with a vision to create a platform where customers can find everything they need in one place. Our founder, inspired by a passion for retail and a desire to offer something unique, started ABC Retail to bring you a curated selection of products and outstanding service.</p>

    <br />

    <h2>Our Mission:</h2>
    <p>Our mission is simple: to make your shopping experience as seamless and enjoyable as possible. We are a dedicated team of 10 professionals working tirelessly to ensure that every aspect of your interaction with us is positive. From our user-friendly website to our responsive customer support, our goal is to provide you with the best solutions for all your needs.</p>

    <br />

    <h2>What Sets Us Apart:</h2>
    <p>We believe in transparency, quality, and service. Our carefully selected range of products is designed to meet the highest standards, and our customer service team is always here to help. Whether you’re looking for the latest trends or classic essentials, we strive to offer a shopping experience that exceeds your expectations.</p>

    <br />

    <h2>Contact Us:</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, don’t hesitate to reach out to us. We’re here to help you with any inquiries you may have.</p>
</div>
